Package: quiltr
Title: Automated website creation from scattered HTML
Version: 0.4.11
Authors@R: "Zachary Foster <zacharyfoster1989@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Tools for making websites from HTML files scattered throughout a directory structure. The hierarchical menu of the website can be derived from HTML file names/paths or custom configuration files.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.0)
License: Creative Commons
LazyData: true
Imports: knitr,
    lubridate,
    plyr,
    xtable,
    plotrix,
    ggplot2,
    packrat,
    rmarkdown,
    yaml,
    rstudioapi,
    XML,
    stringr,
    reshape2,
    devtools
Suggests: testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
